Manchester United manager David Moyes is fired and player-coach Ryan Giggs takes charge on an interim basis. Moyes' dismissal comes 10 months after he succeeded Sir Alex Ferguson. (BBC)(Independent)In tennis, American Serena Williams defeats Maria Sharapova of Russia in straight sets in the Women's Singles final. It is the sixth Australian Open crown and 19th Grand Slam singles title for the current world #1. (AAP via MSN) (The Guardian)